### ============================================
### API 1: Favorite Number Validation
### ============================================

### Test 1.1: Valid Request - Should return 200 OK
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "a8836583-59ee-4bf8-8fa7-9013af8459ae",
  "favNum": 42
}

### Test 1.2: Invalid UUID - Should return 400 with validation error
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "not-a-valid-uuid",
  "favNum": 42
}

### Test 1.3: Missing userId - Should return 400 with validation error
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "favNum": 99
}

### Test 1.4: Zero favNum - Should return 400 (must be > 0)
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "a87666a3-9952-4b51-8a23-5ba543fb87eb",
  "favNum": 0
}

### Test 1.5: Negative favNum - Should return 400 (must be > 0)
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "a717febd-bc30-47b4-97af-94a48fc67cce",
  "favNum": -5
}

### Test 1.6: Invalid JSON Syntax - Should return 400 with "json not valid"
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/favorite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "7f4a4135-183a-4083-ad2a-d0c82126b642",
  "favNum": 42,
}

### ============================================
### API 2: Pet Name Validation
### ============================================

### Test 2.1: Valid Pet Name - Should return 200 OK
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "Fluffy",
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

### Test 2.2: Valid Pet Name with longer name
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "Mr. Whiskers the Third",
  "ownerId": "08088728-50c2-417d-a010-5769965a885c"
}

### Test 2.3: Pet Name too short (< 2 chars) - Should return 400
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "A",
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

### Test 2.4: Pet Name too long (> 50 chars) - Should return 400
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "This is a very long pet name that exceeds the maximum allowed length of fifty characters",
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

### Test 2.5: Missing petName - Should return 400
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

### Test 2.6: Invalid ownerId UUID - Should return 400
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "Buddy",
  "ownerId": "invalid-uuid"
}

### Test 2.7: Empty petName - Should return 400
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "",
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

### Test 2.8: Invalid JSON - Should return 400 with "json not valid"
POST http://localhost:1323/api/v1/pet-name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petName": "Fluffy"
  "ownerId": "f003d47c-e657-485b-a01e-065d18f87295"
}

